{"alquran":{"no":101,"name":"Al-Qaari'a","arab":"القارعة","start":6157,"count":11,"rukku":1,"type":"mecca","description":"Surat ini terdiri atas 11 ayat, termasuk golongan surat-surat Makkiyyah, diturunkan sesudah surat Quraisy. Nama <i>Al Qaari'ah</i> diambil dari kata <i>Al Qaari'ah</i> yang terdapat pada ayat pertama, artinya mengetok dengan keras, kemudian kata ini dipakai untuk nama hari kiamat."},"surah":[{"no":1,"arab":" الْقَارِعَةُ","latin":"alqaari'atu","translate":{"id":"Hari Kiamat,\n","en":"OH, the sudden calamity!"},"audio":{"primary":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6158","secondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6158.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6158.mp3"]}},{"no":2,"arab":"مَا الْقَارِعَةُ","latin":"maa alqaari'atu","translate":{"id":"apakah hari Kiamat itu?\n","en":"How awesome the sudden calamity!"},"audio":{"primary":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6159","secondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6159.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6159.mp3"]}},{"no":3,"arab":"وَمَا أَدْرَاكَ مَا الْقَارِعَةُ","latin":"wamaa adraaka maa alqaari'atu","translate":{"id":"Tahukah kamu apakah hari Kiamat itu?\n","en":"And what could make thee conceive what that sudden calamity will be?"},"audio":{"primary":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6160","secondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6160.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/6160.mp3"]}},{"no":4,"arab":"يَوْمَ يَكُونُ النَّاسُ كَالْفَرَاشِ الْمَبْثُوثِ","latin":"yawma yakuunu alnnaasu kaalfaraasyi almabtsuutsi","translate":{"id":"Pada hari itu manusia adalah seperti anai-anai yang bertebaran,\n","en":"[It will occur] on the Day when men will be like moths swarming in confusion,"},"audio":{"primary":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6161","secondary":["https://cdn.islami